---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About — Plint">
  <section class="page-hero section-dark">
    <div class="page-hero-img">
      <img src="/images/site/about-bg.jpg" alt="" />
    </div>
    <div class="page-hero-text container">
      <h1>Our story</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="story section-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <p>
        For over 25 years, Plint has been at the heart of media localisation, shaping the industry from the days of DVDs to today&rsquo;s AI-driven workflows. Founded by linguists with a deep passion for storytelling, we&rsquo;ve subtitled millions of minutes, dubbed countless hours of content, and helped bring stories to life in over 100 languages.
      </p>
      <p>
        But we&rsquo;re more than a localisation provider — we&rsquo;re pioneers in how localisation is done. By combining decades of linguistic expertise with cutting-edge technology, we don&rsquo;t just translate content; we transform the way it&rsquo;s localised.
      </p>
      <p>
        With a dedicated in-house team of experts: project managers, developers, sound-engineers and strategists, alongside a vast network of talented freelancers, we continue to challenge the status quo — blending creativity with innovation to set new industry standards.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="commitment">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Our commitment to a sustainable future</h2>
      <p>
        At Plint, we believe localisation has the power to bring people together — but it must be done responsibly. We&rsquo;re committed to building a sustainable future for our industry, our people, and the planet.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 70vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    color: var(--color-fg-on-dark);
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #000;
  }
  .page-hero-img { position: absolute; inset: 0; opacity: 0.7; }
  .page-hero-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
  .page-hero-text {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 0 2rem 4rem;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .page-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 7rem);
    line-height: 1;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .story {
    padding: 6rem 0;
  }
  .story .container {
    max-width: 60ch;
  }
  .story p {
    font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 1.4vw, 1.4rem);
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin-bottom: 1.5em;
  }
  .commitment {
    padding: 8rem 0;
    background: #f3f3f3;
  }
  .commitment .container {
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .commitment h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 4rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }
  .commitment p {
    font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 1.4vw, 1.4rem);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
</style>
